e spacing */\n  }\n\n  .inline-list.payment-icons {\n    flex-wrap: wrap; /* Ensure icons wrap nicely */\n    gap: 0px; /* Reduced consistent spacing for mobile */\n  }\n\n  .icon--payment {\n    margin: 0; /* Remove individual margins for better control */\n    transform: scale(1.2); /* Maintain reduced icon size */\n  }\n\n  .icon--payment svg {\n    width: 30px; /* Slightly smaller on mobile for better fit */\n    height: 15px; /* Slightly smaller on mobile for better fit */\n  }\n}\n</style>"
