            "content": "<p>At Ella & Rose, we are here for you 24/7. Our dedicated customer service team is always ready to assist you with any questions or concerns. Feel free to use the contact form on our website or send an email to <strong>info@ellarosedallas.com</strong>. We strive to respond within 48 hours.</p>",
