      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_8hf3pM": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "4-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>Fast delivery and beautifully packaged. The cardigan I ordered looks chic and is perfect for layering. I’ll definitely be ordering again for the autumn season.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/1_58861f66-f611-495e-a8b0-4914ecb151cb.png",
            "author": "Jessica M.",
            "author_info": "Los Angeles"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_MHrxQM": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "4-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>Very impressed! The material feels luxurious but lightweight. It’s stylish without being too much, and I’ve been wearing it to work and at weekends. Brilliant find.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4_03d02788-7d17-4942-b02f-128cce5efa68.png",
            "author": "Amanda K.",
            "author_info": "New York"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_JThjxE": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "5-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>I was a little unsure about sizing, but the guide was accurate. The jacket fits perfectly and is so flattering. Great customer service as well when I had a quick question.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2_82ddfc93-923c-49ce-bbbf-228cc6892ed9.png",
            "author": "Rebecca L.",
            "author_info": "Dallas"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_LMjjFW": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "4-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>The leopard print jacket is a real statement piece! Comfortable, trendy and gets noticed everywhere I go. Love that it’s easy to dress up or down.</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/5.png",
            "author": "Courtney A.",
            "author_info": "Houston"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_THfL8P": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "4-stars",
            "testimonial": "<p>I absolutely love my new coat from Ella & Rose. The fit is spot on and the quality is even better than I expected. It feels elegant yet so easy to wear. Already had compliments!</p>",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3.png",
            "author": "Melissa T.",
            "author_info": "Dallas"
          }
        }
      },
