omfortable all day long.\n                  </p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n    \n  <div class=\"column1\">\n          <div class=\"content-block\">\n            <div class=\"icon-wrapper\">\n              <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/2707/0176/files/ICONOantibacterianoMOVIMIENTO.gif?v=1632989458\" alt=\"\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n               <p><strong>Odor-free</strong><br>\n                    Neutralizes the bacteria that cause body odor when we sweat.\n                  </p>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n    \n</div>",
